            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Sabemos como repetir código usando um loop <code>while</code>. Como este programa que repete instruções para exibir a Bandeira Americana.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"first_counter = \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" first_counter &lt; \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;**********---------&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  first_counter += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"second_counter = \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" second_counter &lt; \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;-------------------&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  second_counter += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
