          },
          {
            "title": "For loop",
            "id": 79131,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para criar um loop <code>for</code> como este, adicionamos a palavra-chave <code>for</code>, uma variável como <code>i</code>, a palavra <code>in</code> e, finalmente, <code>range():</code></p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range():\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"5\" /><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option startIndex=\"9\" endIndex=\"17\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>for</code> seguido de <code>i</code> e depois <code>in</code>, <code>range():</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "For loop",
            "id": 79130,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Em um loop <code>for</code>, podemos especificar quantas vezes gostaríamos que nosso loop fosse executado com a instrução <code>range()</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" range(\" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Happy birthday to you!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"9\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"for\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"while\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Happy birthday to you!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Happy birthday to you!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Happy birthday to you!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Happy birthday to you!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Happy birthday to you!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>range</code>.</p></body></html>"
